0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T13:08:31.000Z","msg":"可惜係做左咁多野，都比人話只有弊無利<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a06122471bb82a979aebe243e44ee9853ced382e","tid":2126990,"uid":79410,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T13:18:23.000Z","msg":"支那收人錢. <br />\n日日反美, 反英, 反美.<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"347f922d9edd8ca5bbcd9c2e805548bc41f40709","tid":2126990,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T14:28:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"107c3a190712e3475ba93d1a6dd9ebacbcd6ab40","tid":2126990,"uid":80724,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T14:34:23.000Z","msg":"亞洲之中真係最想日台戒到人民幣毒<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n台灣已經好成功，繼續就得<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果日本戒到就正，寧願係日本見到多啲鬼佬都唔想見到支那人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />無支那人嘅日本一定更加正"},{"pid":"8619a879fe3c24b5c59e16f0d82d536570724dcd","tid":2126990,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T19:49:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9f353e98c692743577293a381f4d254510a2336","tid":2126990,"uid":43173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9ecf220387939a3486d6806237bc46f2f32cc80d","tid":2126990,"uid":22675,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T06:14:53.000Z","msg":"可說是助紂為虐呀。<br />\n日、美應該很後悔自己親手養大這個曾經傾力幫助的惡魔國，導致現在反過來狠咬猛殺。<br />\n倒是尚有有德、韓、法等國依舊混沌不清，仍然執意要與惡魔打交道，以為信了惡魔可以得永生⋯⋯。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T20:31:16.000Z","msg":"所以話你美日 搬石頭砸自己腳 冇錯"}]}